# Template — Input Requirements

Provide the following where available:

- Contract name and date
- Contract type
- Party being advised
- Upstream or downstream position
- Governing law and jurisdiction
- Procurement stage: bid, preferred tenderer, award, post-award
- Risk appetite
- Key commercial objectives
- Key known sensitivities
- Whether a departures schedule is required
- Whether summary only or full review is required
- Full contract text, or list of missing documents if incomplete
